## Cloning Process

1. **Read the analysis** - Understand structure, components, design tokens
2. **Set up theme** - Create/update theme with extracted colors and typography
3. **Build atoms first** - Buttons, inputs, text styles
4. **Build molecules** - Cards, form groups, nav items
5. **Build organisms** - Header, hero, feature sections
6. **Compose page** - Put sections together
7. **Add responsiveness** - Implement breakpoint behavior
8. **Add interactions** - Hover states, animations

